âœ… 1. Create a Database (DB) in Notion

You have two ways: inline or full page.


---

A. Create an Inline Database (inside your page)

1. Open your page (e.g., Arrays â€“ Patterns).


2. Type:
/table inline


3. Hit Enter â†’ a small table appears right inside the page.


4. Rename it (click title): Array Patterns.




