B. Create a Full-Page Database

1. In the sidebar, click + New Page.


2. Click Table â†’ Full Page.


3. Name it, e.g., DSA Problems DB.



This creates a database page that behaves like a dedicated spreadsheet.


---

âœ… 2. Add / Edit Columns

